node.text: I used the @ghd_northamerica rise hot brush to give myself a blow out. I love that this tool refreshes the hair and gives you a lot of volume! I recommend holding the brush down when working on your hair in the front and hold the brush facing up when styling your hair in the back #ghdrise #ghdhair

node.text: I just uploaded a nutrition and fitness update on my YouTube channel. I started the keto diet about 2 years ago and It changed my life! It taught me to understand and value proper nutrition. With the help of @workingagainstgravity  I transitioned off keto and into a balanced diet. I’ve learned to love CARBS. I have a better understanding of balance and how important food is in this fitness journey. Link to my YouTube video is in my bio ❤️
